perconductor. The transition temperatures found varies from\n2.7 to 7 K. This information and other results will be presented in this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2015 20:19:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-31"}
