wind activities which were initiated\n$\\sim$10$^2$ Myr ago formed the extended ionized gas nebula of NGC 6240.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Dec 2015 03:53:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
